description:
&lt;p&gt;Play days Day Nursery is based on site at James Cook University Hospital and is registered by OFSTED the Early Years directorate to cater for 86 children a day. The age range covers children from 6 weeks until school age.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The nursery is open from 6.45am until 6.00pm Monday to Friday for 52 weeks throughout the year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a dedicated Nursery Assistant who will be key in providing education and care for a group of children, liaising with parents and who will provide high quality child care. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for childcare and the development of children&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An excellent understanding of the Early Years Foundation Stages and safe guarding responsibilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good communication and interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to assist in the provision of a stimulating and creative environment for children aged 6 weeks to 5 years&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A caring approach to the individual needs of children&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you do then come and be a part of our friendly and professional team who share your passion for delivering the Early Years foundation stage to the highest standards through working in partnership with parents and safeguarding children. Previous experience of working within a day nursery setting would be welcome.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note this post will close at sufficient applicants&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameClare McAllenJob titleNursery ManagerEmail addressclare.mcallen@nhs.netTelephone number01642 282810Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion about the post please contact the Nursery Managers on 01642 282810.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
